      <h1 itemprop="headline">Why Most People Struggle to Turn Ideas Into Videos</h1>

      <div class="meta" aria-label="Article metadata">
        <span><strong>By</strong> <span itemprop="author">Rob Franco</span></span>
        <span><strong>Published</strong> <time datetime="2026-04-18" itemprop="datePublished">April 18, 2026</time></span>
        <span><strong>Site</strong> Happiness in the Digital Age</span>
      </div>

